from typing import List, Union
from accessor import getValue, setValue

image_1_url ='https://assets-global.website-files.com/612770618d97595db63a9470/61de87e4e5669c8f2ee9a0f5_Player-tracking(Checked-with-David-H.jpg'
image_2_url = 'https://assets-global.website-files.com/612770618d97595db63a9470/61de8823f093475813c41e1d_Poses-and-actions-(Checked-with-David).jpg'

toggle = 1

def on_change_image_click(path: List[Union[str, int]]):
    global toggle
    if (toggle == 1):
        setValue(['image'], image_2_url)
        toggle = 2
    elif (toggle == 2):
        setValue(['image'], image_1_url)
        toggle = 1

    return
